#: ../../09-old.rst:33
msgid "模型的数据是如何生成的？"
msgstr "How is the model data generated?"

#: ../../09-old.rst:35
msgid "详见： https://github.com/fxsjy/jieba/issues/7"
msgstr "See details: https://github.com/fxsjy/jieba/issues/7"

#: ../../09-old.rst:37
msgid "“台中”总是被切成“台 中”？（以及类似情况）"
msgstr "\"Taichung\" is always segmented into \"Tai Chung\"? (and similar cases)"

#: ../../09-old.rst:39
msgid "P(台中) ＜ P(台)×P(中)，“台中”词频不够导致其成词概率较低"
msgstr "P(Taichung) < P(Tai) × P(Chung); the frequency of \"Taichung\" is not enough, resulting in a lower probability of forming a word."

#: ../../09-old.rst:41
msgid "解决方法：强制调高词频"
msgstr "Solution: Forcefully increase the word frequency"

#: ../../09-old.rst:43
msgid "`jieba.add_word('台中')` 或者 `jieba.suggest_freq('台中', True)`"
msgstr "`jieba.add_word('台中')` or `jieba.suggest_freq('台中', True)`"

#: ../../09-old.rst:45
msgid "“今天天气 不错”应该被切成“今天 天气 不错”？（以及类似情况）"
msgstr "\"Today's weather is good\" should be segmented as \"Today weather good\"? (and similar cases)"

#: ../../09-old.rst:47
msgid "解决方法：强制调低词频"
msgstr "Solution: Forcefully decrease the word frequency"

#: ../../09-old.rst:49
msgid "`jieba.suggest_freq(('今天', '天气'), True)`"
msgstr "`jieba.suggest_freq(('今天', '天气'), True)`"

#: ../../09-old.rst:51
msgid "或者直接删除该词 `jieba.del_word('今天天气')`"
msgstr "Or delete the word directly: `jieba.del_word('今天天气')`"

#: ../../09-old.rst:53
msgid "切出了词典中没有的词语，效果不理想？"
msgstr "Segmented words that are not in the dictionary, with unsatisfactory results?"

#: ../../09-old.rst:55
msgid "解决方法：关闭新词发现"
msgstr "Solution: Disable new word discovery"

#: ../../09-old.rst:57
msgid "`jieba.cut('丰田太省了', HMM=False)` `jieba.cut('我们中出了一个叛徒', HMM=False)`"
msgstr "`jieba.cut('丰田太省了', HMM=False)` `jieba.cut('我们中出了一个叛徒', HMM=False)`"

